                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Do you want to develop your upper back but don’t know where to start? Then you need to try the seated wide-grip cable row. This back shredding exercise will help sculpt and define your physique.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Today, we discuss how to do the seated wide-grip cable row. We cover proper technique, anatomy, expert tips, and programming to help you increase your upper body muscle mass.</span></p>                    </div>
