                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Brachialis</p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Muscle which starts at the middle of your upper arm and connects just below the elbow.</p></p>
                                </div>
                                                            <div class="secondary-item muscle-item">
                                    <div class="muscle-img">
                                        <img src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Brachioradialis.png" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Brachioradialis</p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Muscle located between outside portion of your forearm from the elbow to the wrist.</p></p>
                                </div>
                                                            <div class="secondary-item muscle-item">
                                    <div class="muscle-img">
                                        <img src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rear-Deltoid.png" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Posterior Deltoid</p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Muscles located at the back of your shoulder. Helps with posture.</p></p>
                                </div>
